text: is a Japanese football player. She played for the Japan national team. ==Biography== Kunitake was born in Yamato, Kumamoto on January 10, 1997. After graduating from Musashigaoka College, she joined Nadeshiko League club Nojima Stella Kanagawa Sagamihara in 2017. She became a regular player as center back and played all league matches until 2019. In 2020, she moved to Mynavi Vegalta Sendai.Mynavi Vegalta Sendai On July 29, 2018, Kunitake debuted for the Japan national team against Brazil. She also played at 2018 Asian Games and Japan won the champions.
